stylometry: Data mining is when you search through a large amount of information on a spreadsheet to find trends and simalarities between that information shown. It is important in business because data mining does show the trends between information. So say you want to come out with a new product and want it to be extremely succesful out in the market. You could use data mining to see what is popular amoung the market to help you think of something that would sell. Also you could use data mining to find out where the economy is picking up by seeing trends of more spending and a greater demand for certain products.
